reviewText: My 3 year old son loves this show.
My 2 year old loves this video he watches it over and over he just can't get enough of it
This DVD came and only half of the episodes are watchable on disc one due to all the scratches on the disc.  Disc 2 also has scratches, but so far has worked fine.
For a 3 year old and 1 year old this is a fun show they will watch over and over so I got entire season to watch in the car.
This ia a cute show for young children, my 2 and 3 year old boys enjoy it.  It promotes positive thinking and values and is cute.
